Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:04.47,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this system at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:09.13,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't making us clean up when \Nthe date matches our student number
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:11.15,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,let students in the 30s off the hook?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:17.11,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yakishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.99,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.95,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, this sort of thing foreshadows\N a very arousing turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.46,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But in rom-com terms, \NYakishio and I are short on plot developments
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.94,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,that would lead to an incident \Nin the gym storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.83,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened with that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.80,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What "thing" do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.94,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:54.65,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki said he was gonna borrow books \Nfrom the lit club. Did he do that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.40,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that "thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:02.73,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I-If it's okay, I wouldn't mind \Ntaking the books to him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.28,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about this:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:14.47,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we get him to pick them up\Nwhen you have a day off from your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.22,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,My club? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:21.77,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, because it'd probably be okay\N for you to visit the lit club then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.89,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,As an observer or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:27.46,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,An observer? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.81,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I mean, you could even \Ncome to the club together then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.02,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you. Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.96,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Nukumizu, you're really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.20,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually not such a bad guy.\N I had you all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I think the entire class has me all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:50.41,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.46,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.87,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:57.15,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,the door might be locked from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:57.96,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.96,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.01,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.01,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.13,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.13,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:11.61,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,The forecast said the temperature \Nwas gonna get up to 35 degrees today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.74,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first really hot day of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.18,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. She must have a super fast metabolism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.35,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yakishio-san, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:27.94,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I'm more like an impala\Nthan a Thomson's gazelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.90,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're an impala?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.92,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's a lot faster to run on four legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:41.63,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is, spotted hyenas \Nlike to get splashed with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.36,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,She definitely doesn't sound okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.63,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yakishio-san, here! It's a cooling spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.27,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Nuk-kun, nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.89,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Am I "Nuk-kun" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.47,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Spray it all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.27,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.17,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.65,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the day would come \Nwhen a girl was begging for me!
