Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.72,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.08,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:43.44,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,you can't blame me if I start getting\Nin a weird mood. This isn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.82,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! Don't take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.84,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Nuk-kun, what's the big deal?\N It's just us girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.25,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely out of her mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.22,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,This bottle still has something in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.27,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Y-You can't drink that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.97,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nuk-kun, whaddaya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.55,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yakishio-san! Your top! Your top!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:16.14,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Something's touching me! \NSomething's touching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.94,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is somebody in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.27,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.64,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.21,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Catch ya when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.87,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.68,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.67,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. It's so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:54.79,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,Heatstroke is really scary. Worst-case, \Nit can leave you disabled or even kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.97,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Forget class, you guys. \NJust rest here in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:02.63,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,And you, mister. I'll contact your homeroom \Nteacher. Name and class number?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.38,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your class, Sensei. It's me, Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.65,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.63,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.32,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Konuki-chan. \NI'll let you take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:18.03,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Konuki-sensei, are you and \NAmanatsu-sensei close friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.08,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:24.88,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,We used to be classmates here and spent \Na lot of time in the nurse's office together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.32,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,The stains on the ceiling \Nhaven't changed at all since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.81,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you remember \Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.09,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when you get laid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:37.01,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, when you're leaning back, \Nthe ceiling's right there in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.70,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,This lady is kinda nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.62,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.32,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.48,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.42,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I brought your bento lunch. Wanna eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.27,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Am I in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:09.51,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll step out for a bit, so you \Ncan go ahead and use the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:13.32,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can lock it from the inside.\N Enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:17.76,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,First Amanatsu-sensei, now her. \NHow did they even become teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.90,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Omelet rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:25.55,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm pretty proud of this one. \NI was able to flip it and roll it nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.65,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, hands together. \NThank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.87,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:38.07,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good, right? \NSo how much is it worth to you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:40.49,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Let's say 400 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.25,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Not too shabby. But I'm gonna \Nstep up to that 400 yen wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.92,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,and smash through it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:51.39,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Your strategy is to add soup\N to raise the assessed value.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.63,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever in the world made you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.59,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,that this is soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.83,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's white sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:05.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Personally speaking, I prefer ketchup, \Nbut the extra effort does add flair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.64,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:17.11,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,It was left over from a holiday present I got.\NIt's the Empire Hotel's official white sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:23.44,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,So? How much would you pay for this flavor?\N For a taste of the Empire Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:27.72,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.21,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,600 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.71,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(100,147,235,150)\pos(168,184.667)\fad(100,0)\fnCourier New\b1\bord1.5\shad0\fscx85\fs40\3c&H3C3423&\c&HECEBE0&}Balance
