Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.71,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,600 yen! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:35.17,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you guys are having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:39.18,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lemon-chan! Good morning. \NAre you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.98,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Much, much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:45.18,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember what happened \Nat the end. How did we end up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.64,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um, no, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.88,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amanatsu-sensei rescued us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:50.93,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.39,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess Amanatsu-sensei \Nchanged my clothes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:56.84,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Amanatsu-sensei \Nchanged your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.20,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't see a thing. Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.03,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not have. What sort\Nof creep watches a girl changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.01,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun, that's kinda gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. \NI won't be able to face another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:11.28,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, what's that? It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.60,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? I made it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.18,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Say "ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.88,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she feeding her from my plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.85,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, yum! What is this sauce? It's so wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.30,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Why, it's from the Empire Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.50,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's actually my lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.87,Top,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire Hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.32,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nuk-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.17,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I guess that counts\N as an indirect kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.39,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Mind out of the gutter, son. You're at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:36.99,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking anything dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.64,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then why are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.18,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.36,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Is Lemon here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.62,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:48.50,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling better? Here. \NI brought you a get-well gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.05,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,You brought this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.99,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,But you seem fine. Maybe you don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:57.36,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I do! I was feeling so bad, \NI couldn't eat at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.22,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.79,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat it if it's on your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.97,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.52,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.70,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chihaya. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:15.52,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of going to the study room \Nafter class. Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.99,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Gotta go home early today. \NI'll see you at cram school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:23.97,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Then I'll get in touch later tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.75,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Silly. I said I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.09,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get back to class. \NLemon, take it easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.04,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure. Thanks.
