Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.14,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fax-0.38\fscy110\blur0.3\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fscx55\fs13\c&HCEE4D3&\frx350\fry2\frz359.4\pos(638,288)}The Complete Works\N{\fs16\fscx65}of Abe Kobo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.32,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Tsukinoki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.40,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.10,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I lend \Nsome of these to a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:53.12,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I don't mind. \NButter him up with favors,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:56.30,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,then once he's cornered, we recruit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.32,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.37,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:06.32,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro keeps forgetting the \Nduty schedule and has to stay after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.24,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go give him backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:12.21,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Just don't lay a finger \Non the Dazai or Mishima, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.67,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro? Huh. Must be her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.44,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.46,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Not her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.72,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a ch-childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.05,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,A-And she got the order wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.23,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\an7\bord0\fs20\shad0\blur0.3\c&H9BEDF0&\frz13.22\pos(102.667,92)\frx8\fry0}Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.23,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\an7\bord0\b1\fs22\fscx90\fax0.00\shad0\blur0.3\c&H454B4C&\frz13.22\pos(55.333,177.334)\iclip(m 218 266 l 356 116 296 49 577 17 610 178)}Mishima comes first! Mishima, Dazai is the correct order!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.23,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\an7\bord0\b1\fs22\fscx90\fax0.00\shad0\blur0.3\c&H2B3132&\frz13.22\pos(55.333,177.334)\clip(m 218 266 l 356 116 296 49 577 17 610 178)}Mishima comes first! Mishima, Dazai is the correct order!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.64,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares either way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.15,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\\fnArial\pos(212.667,99.334)\c&H444038&\frx4\fry4\frz18.52}Tamaki Shintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.15,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\c&H444038&\frz18.52\pos(250,116)\frx12\fry4}See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.15,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\c&H444038&\frz18.52\frx12\fry4\pos(298,182.333)}Welcome again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.15,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fax0.05\fs12\c&H444038&\pos(375.333,201.333)\frz19.02\frx6\fry4}Let me know when you're planning to butter him up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:40.36,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I could almost pass for a \Nregular high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.55,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kaju? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:49.27,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, have you made \Nany friends at school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:51.51,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.37,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:57.93,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,People aren't allowed to be \Ncompletely friendless after middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.84,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning I'm not allowed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:04.78,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,For example, excluding teachers, \Nhow many people did you talk to today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:08.64,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... five people, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:10.81,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Five people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:19.86,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I feel awful for hounding you so much \Nthat you feel you have to lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:25.15,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, having no friends is \Nreally nothing to be ashamed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.82,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But it still isn't allowed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.97,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\p1\an7\shad0\blur0.3\bord1\fscx150\fscy80\1a&H20&\pos(15,15)\3c&H5F8585&\c&HE1F1EC&}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
