Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.97,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\fscx90\c&H4B41D3&\pos(483,55)}Congratulations {\c&H676C6B&\fs10.2}on being selected\Nto participate in the national high\N school tennis competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.01,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Nuk-kun, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.45,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, g-good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.85,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I finally remembered what happened\N in the storage room yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.12,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,So today, after class—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.85,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Y-You remembered what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.27,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I didn't see! \NI didn't see anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:04.66,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,What? We talked about me going \Nto the lit club with Mitsuki today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.24,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:09.86,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say we should come together? \NDid the heat fry your brain, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.97,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Yeah, I totally did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.70,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.54,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.96,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan sure is going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:26.30,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(135,213,269,216)\pos(202.667,251.333)\fnCourier New\b1\bord1.5\shad0\fscx85\fs40\3c&H3C3423&\c&HECEBE0&}Balance
