Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:24.05,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should come observe, too,\N so I can back her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:27.36,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but to the literature club?\N Are you cool with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.93,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Heh. I really like flowers and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.34,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the horticulture club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:32.88,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.77,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\fs18\fax-0.4\shad0\blur0.3\fnGeorgia\b1\fscx90\c&H152019&\pos(230.667,83.334)\frz32.55}\hLit Before\NYou Leap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.77,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nukumizu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.03,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.81,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tamaki Shintaro, the club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.90,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So Shintaro was the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.90,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.25,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this your Abe Kobo friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:50.11,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs9\fnGeorgia\b1\c&H020500&\frz25.15\pos(574.667,112.667)}All Deadlines\NAre Bad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.78,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, actually, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:50.11,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. My name's Yanami, \Nnot Abe. I've come to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:54.82,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm happy so many people \Nare interested in the lit club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:56.08,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I tried wool felting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.29,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Where you poke a hairball with a needle.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.93,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the knit club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.62,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs9\fnArial\pos(374,317.333)\c&H0B2518&}New club member!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.93,0:15:00.73,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:00.75,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs9.5\fnArial\c&H0B2518&\pos(377.333,300)}New club member!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:04.29,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go attend a presidents' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.75,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10.2\fnArial\c&H0B2518&\pos(377.333,284.667)}New club member!
