Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:02.75,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur1.5\fs23\fnArial\c&H0B2518&\pos(369.6,292)}New club member!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.28,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.21,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs9\fnGeorgia\b1\c&H020500&\frz25.15\pos(574.667,112.667)}All Deadlines\NAre Bad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.81,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That sci-fi book I borrowed \Nwas really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.88,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really get it, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.18,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,You thought so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.58,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I knew you had good taste, Komari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.47,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.05,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Komari-chan, if you don't like that,\N I'll tell him off myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.33,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.15,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,My head... d-doesn't really... uh, hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.70,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a cutie, Komari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.01,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn from her example, Koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.00,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Shaddap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.41,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:43.93,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,The p-president... He called... \NHe called me a c-cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.17,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You two sure get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.63,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're childhood friends. \NWe're kinda stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.91,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Childhood friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.35,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.31,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Homewrecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:04.15,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cmon, Yanami-san.\NLet's not use that talk in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:04.90,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.11,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.69,Top,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon, behave yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:11.08,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano. Nice timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:17.66,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,This really is an outstanding collection.\N Which one should I borrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.63,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Take whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:24.68,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,But if you decide to join our club, you'll be \Nable to borrow anything freely. Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.54,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I am interested, \Nbut I'm busy with cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:32.76,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's no problem. You can come \Nand borrow books whenever you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.62,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe your cute \Ngirlfriend wants to join, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.92,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.17,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean me when you say "girlfriend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:45.52,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh! But I'm in the track club,\N so that might be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.92,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk, tsk, tsk. We're totally open\N to dual memberships.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.48,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, all of our members \Nare in other clubs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:55.03,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? What other club am I in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:59.19,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,You can come hide here if you \Never want to skip track practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:03.23,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Right? And wouldn't it be nice to have \Nmore time to spend with your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.53,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Would you like that, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.97,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be fair to Lemon. \NWe aren't dating, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.31,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:16.30,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been really popular with \Nthe guys. I wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.84,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks for letting me borrow—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.22,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:25.58,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a boyfriend, and being popular\N doesn't mean I'd go with just anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.19,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.57,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.54,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:37.78,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.43,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,What's this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:44.53,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you two aren't dating? \NYou sure act like a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.83,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, we don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.54,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.89,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,But we aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.38,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. And I already have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:18:00.26,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H30&\t(1200,1700,\alpha&HAB&)\t(1748,1749,\alpha&H35&)\t(2850,3250,\alpha&HAE&)\t(3289,3290,\alpha&H40&)\t(4000,4400,\alpha&HBA&)\t(4450,4451,\alpha&H50&)\t(5100,5400,\alpha&HCA&)\t(5460,5461,\alpha&H70&)\t(6000,6300,\alpha&HDA&)\t(6375,6376,\alpha&H90&)\t(7200,7500,\alpha&HFF&)}I already have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.72,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.45,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:10.46,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um, Mitsuki... You got a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:14.15,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just recently. \NI guess I hadn't told you yet, Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.03,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess. Is it Asagumo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.45,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Was it that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:22.00,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. I'll introduce \Nyou guys properly next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.79,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Lemon. Wanna get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.70,Default,Koto; Nukumizu; Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.16,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to go \Nshopping together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:31.63,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Is Ayano actually totally dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:36.80,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've decided to join the lit club, \Nso I think I'll hang out here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.34,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Then I guess I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.09,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Was that maybe... my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.64,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.85,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.75,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme an application form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.36,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fax-0.35\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\b1\fnArial\fs22\pos(625.6,12.8)\frz1.096\c&H18261F&}Club Application
