Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.36,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fax-0.45\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fnGeorgia\fs15\fscy90\c&H97A3A5&\pos(212.8,68)\frz359}I'd like to {\alpha&HFF&\t(1567,1568,\alpha&H00&)}j{\alpha&HFF&\t(1649,1650,\alpha&H00&)}o{\alpha&HFF&\t(1734,1735,\alpha&H00&)}i{\alpha&HFF&\t(1815,1816,\alpha&H00&)}n {\alpha&HFF&\t(1899,1900,\alpha&H00&)}t{\c&H6E7F70&\alpha&HFF&\t(1982,1983,\alpha&H00&)}h{\alpha&HFF&\t(2065,2066,\alpha&H00&)}e
