Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.36,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fax-0.35\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fnGeorgia\fs15\c&H41564C&\pos(600.8,141.6)\frz357}August 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.36,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fax-0.38\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\b1\fnArial\fs14\c&H18261F&\frz354.8\pos(192.8,176.8)}Name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.36,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fax-0.35\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fnGeorgia\fs20\fscy90\c&H6B7C77&\frz355.1\pos(222.4,155.2)\alpha&HFF&\t(1815,1816,\alpha&H00&)}Y{\alpha&HFF&\t(1899,1900,\alpha&H00&)}a{\alpha&HFF&\t(2057,2058,\alpha&H00&)}k{\alpha&HFF&\t(2147,2148,\alpha&H00&)}i
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.36,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. So Mitsuki already had a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.64,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,What have I been doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.30,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Running in circles, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:09.53,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, welcome. Wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.53,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I will. I'm all worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.17,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,0)\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs7\fscx80\fnArial\c&H0B2518&\pos(298.4,33.6)\frz9.125}New club member!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.13,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs15\fax-0.2\c&H418EB8&\frz14.91\pos(396,146.4)}Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.13,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fscx90\shad0\fax-0.24\fay0.01\fs34\an8\frz14.23\c&HB0BBC3&\3c&H3E3D4B&\pos(374.4,219.2)}Gusto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend basically got dumped, \Nso to cheer her up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:26.26,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,you take her to the restaurant where {\i0}you{\i1} \Ngot dumped? Do you have nerves of steel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:31.36,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, Yanami-san...\NYou're paying for yourself today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:35.98,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! But talking about money in front \Nof a girl who just had her heart broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.95,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no tact at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.42,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan, we'll treat you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.49,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.62,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.21,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating you joining the club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.66,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm gonna have a Hamburg steak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:51.75,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yanami-san, are you okay \Neating that much before dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:56.25,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know? \NSweets are a diet's worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.61,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,And a Hamburg steak\Nbefore dinner is a diet's ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.29,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I think I'll have\N a bean paste sundae.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:05.93,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! \NI think I'll have that for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.56,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought sweets were the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.40,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll add a hamburger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.12,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really eat that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:18.42,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yakishio-san, we'll take care of the bill.\N Go ahead and wait for us outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:23.03,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nuk-kun, Yana-chan. \NOkay, if it's all right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.45,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun, you can be \Npretty thoughtful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:31.55,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,You still owe me. I'm not \Nthe one actually paying today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:36.18,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying. Fine. \NBut I'll tell you something, Nukumizu—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.97,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.85,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you don't \Nhave enough to cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.68,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Is this girl seriously just completely...
