Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.20,Italics,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat it if it's on your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.65,Italics,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thank you—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.80,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,That Nukumizu kid doesn't look \Nlike much, but he's got moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.12,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.76,Italics,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.93,Italics,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chihaya. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:16.86,Italics,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of going to the study room\Nafter class. Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.05,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\c&H7E664B&\b1\fs28\pos(356,140)}STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:26.42,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should set another \None up in the study room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:40.32,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.19,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like running, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.81,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,And my club didn't meet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:49.80,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,You should be heading home. \NI can walk you part of the way if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:55.03,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can I just do one more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.66,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,You want to keep running?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:02.95,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm about to get somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.10,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\blur0.3\fax-0.21\fs30\c&H6B756B&\3c&HDBE4D7&\frx26\fry2\frz334.8\pos(392.8,310.4)}Yakishio
