Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.38,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Go ahead and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:20.98,Default,Konuki,0000,0000,0000,,But give it everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.19,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
